{
  "stem": "21786.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We pulled out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We reported to the SS men at the gate, who simply took our numbers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were sent either to the female camp for blankets, which were repaired there, or we were sent for supplies, medical supplies, or from the oncoming train that we-- I did altogether three times.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a harrowing experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For we were mingled directly with the people who are coming for the selection.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were always interfering.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who says that we wouldn't be passed through the same thing?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it did not happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also, on three occasions, we were sent to something, part of the camp called Kanada.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why they called it Kanada, nobody knows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But probably it was the magnificent Canadian joke, namely, all the merchandise-- everything what came with the transport, which was seized from the prisoners, came to this barracks-- to these barracks.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were about nine of them, and they were sorted, to-- there were thousands of glasses and watches and everything, all in the huge, huge kind of collections.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
